r />\n<br />\n用四個人開四個counter,同兩個counter,兩個人執餐時間會差唔多？"},{"pid":"046d6dc39f2ba68f7644983ff8da9fbefc8f1cfb","tid":150652,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T08:53:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講咁多做咩減價先啦</blockquote><br />\n佢啲飯都平嘅，但我覺得佢哋食物種類太多，而家失晒焦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實都收得皮"},{"pid":"b623e1b96e029e5dbea55fb321415350bb7ad6ad","tid":150652,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T06:40:44.000Z","msg":"KFC簡直係快餐界嘅亞視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c00eda85e302eb8d939ec3313f0f26882d9be6","tid":150652,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T06:43:14.000Z","msg":"Kfc不思進取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e11062380de53e9642c66b4759fe58cc5a590d","tid":150652,"uid":48460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T06:45:17.000Z","msg":"無薯條得薯格<br />\n買麥當勞基本上都係為咗個薯條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9693ae312367f2a0acb344e549c58b037d7d4df3","tid":150652,"uid":12814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T06:47:49.000Z","msg":"啲雞咁撚難食擊條毛咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289e5ebb6d0a0bb83a46f8c986bc199f768f1c71","tid":150652,"uid":41693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T06:51:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實收銀同執雞同1個人真係慳到好多錢?</blockquote><br />\n呢個真係諗唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用四個人開四個counter,同兩個counter,兩個人執餐時間會差唔多？</blockquote><br />\n照道理係<br />\n2+2分工專做收銀/執餐係比較快<br />\n因為慳左走黎走去個時間 而且專做一樣野係可以因為熟練而更快 不過要setup好似麥當勞/新Kfc既系統 收完錢 入面有個screen比入面員工執餐再隊出去 <br />\n要setup唔難 但全港至少有8成或以上店舖都需要轉 <br />\n 裝修都幾係野"},{"pid":"c48219ac666544ac31d797670fa85b724c8e3d36","tid":150652,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep