aces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有野你咪講囉 擺放粒膠好有型？"},{"pid":"3b4eac79d0fd2cd180093212afd1d793a0c24841","tid":150652,"uid":88829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:59:45.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"14fb779478f296260544b6bd6a21d905acfc4b20","tid":150652,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:14:42.000Z","msg":"澳洲KFC個薯條好食啊，有落唔知咩味粉<br />\n香港不如唔好要個薯格啦，轉薯條加味粉<br />\n應該有機會打贏M記"},{"pid":"657fd2c5591af655e5e57fbdc388e07d08956610","tid":150652,"uid":60047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:16:47.000Z","msg":"叫kfc做返好d雞先啦<br />\n成日不務正業"},{"pid":"a7e6f3e05ab6ec1698263ec0193d1d142b091f36","tid":150652,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:18:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫kfc做返好d雞先啦<br />\n成日不務正業</blockquote><br />\n依樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a730fb9af84265b79cf716a332fbcbaed68654","tid":150652,"uid":33788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:30:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫kfc做返好d雞先啦<br />\n成日不務正業</blockquote><br />\n依樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我冇咩要求<br />\n可唔可以A2長註有得揀燒雞<br />\n<br />\n每次出新雞A2就冇得揀雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新雞每次係難食過屎"},{"pid":"93920a51dc94b6ce7a4030c09619f8accb140a7a","tid":150652,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:33:36.000Z","msg":"而家d薯蓉蘑菇飯汁淡過水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"396fc64cd0837c5841fe2efcdd1ace8f285d7dc2","tid":150652,"uid":53773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:35:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家d薯蓉蘑菇飯汁淡過水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br /